statements: SELECT ip_address, timestamp, interaction_type FROM website_data WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT * FROM website_data WHERE page_url = '/home';
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM website_data WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT page_url, timestamp FROM website_data WHERE ip_address = '192.168.1.1';
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM website_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT * FROM website_data WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT ip_address, interaction_type FROM website_data WHERE page_url LIKE '%/products%' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT page_url, COUNT(ip_address) AS total_visits FROM website_data GROUP BY page_url ORDER BY total_visits DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT interaction_type FROM website_data ORDER BY interaction_type;
SELECT page_url, timestamp FROM website_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited, time_spent_seconds FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_date = '2021-10-25' ORDER BY time_spent_seconds DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited, time_spent_seconds FROM website_traffic WHERE time_spent_seconds > 60;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited LIKE '%home%' ORDER BY visit_date DESC;
SELECT interaction_id, visitor_id, interaction_type, interaction_time FROM user_interactions ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE page_visited = 'HomePage' AND time_spent_seconds > 60 ORDER BY visit_date DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, visit_date, page_visited, time_spent_seconds FROM website_traffic WHERE time_spent_seconds < 30 AND page_visited LIKE '%Contact%' ORDER BY visit_date ASC;
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic GROUP BY visitor_id ORDER BY total_visits DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, MAX(time_spent_seconds) AS max_time_spent FROM website_traffic GROUP BY visitor_id ORDER BY max_time_spent DESC;

SELECT visitor_id, visit_date, SUM(time_spent_seconds) AS total_time_spent FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-04-30' GROUP BY visitor_id ORDER BY total_time_spent DESC;
